text: Serrell is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Barney Serrell (1920–1996), American baseball player *Edward W. Serrell (1826–1906), American civil engineer and Civil War veteran *Orlando Serrell (born 1968), American acquired savant *Philip Serrell (born 1954), British auctioneer, antiques expert and television presenter.
